Install Anaconda 2019.07 Python 3.7 version, including
  ‚ÅÉ astropy 3.2.1

Install lmfit version 0.9.14
 https://lmfit.github.io/lmfit-py/installation.html#installation
e.g.,
 conda install -c conda-forge lmfit

Install/upgrade to emcee version 3.0.0
 https://emcee.readthedocs.io/en/latest/user/install/
e.g.,
 pip install emcee --upgrade

Install corner, version 2.0.1 e.g.,
 pip install corner

Install celerite-0.3.1, e.g., 
 conda install -c conda-forge celerite

Install ellc-1.8.5

Upgrade numpy to version numpy-1.17.2, e.g.,
 pip install numpy --upgrade


